  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective is to characterize the pharmacokinetics of single doses of ceftobiprole
      in neonates and infants aged ≤3 months. The secondary objective is to evaluate safety and
      tolerability of ceftobiprole in neonates and infants aged ≤3 months.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
